      <title>哈佛因投资损失而削减 2022 年捐赠基金负责人的薪酬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/harvard-cut-pay-to-endowment-head-narvekar-in-2022-amid-losses</link>
